<br>
I have &quot;noticed&quot; although not parsed that my 2hs prismatic &quot;seems&quot; to proc more than my 1hb prismatic.  It also seems that my Lurid Dagger proc's much more than my Frostbringer (more than the delay difference should indicate) These I do not have scientific evidence of though.  Although the first sentence of my reply should answer your question.<br>
