<br>
I'm sorry... What?<br>
<br>
That implies foreknowedge of the length of a fight and the number of times you're going to swing your weapon. While some of the combat logic in EQ is complicated, I don't think it can predict the future. While I don't have parses to support this, proc'ing seems to be a semi-random event whose overall frequency is determined by several factors, including DEX, haste, and the mysterious "proc rate" of the weapon. Just because you haven't proc'ed recently doesn't make you any more likely to proc on your next swing, nor does having just proc'ed make it unlikely you'll proc again.<br>
<br>
Yaen B`zhen<br>
